							<tr>
								<td valign="top" width="400">
									<font face="arial, helvetica, sanserif" size="2">
									<p>
						Elizabeth Inness-Brown is the author of two
						collections of short stories, <i>Satin Palms</i>
						and <i>Here</i>. Raised in the North Country of
						New York State, she now lives with her husband
						and young son on South Hero, an island in Lake
						Champlain, Vermont. 
					<br>
					<br><font size="-1" color="gray">Photo (c) Jane Myers</font><br><br>

									</font>
